' ____ RELATIONS BETWEEN CLASSES _____________________________________________
' <|--      extension
' *--       composition
' o--       aggregation

' Figure <|-- Point
Figure <|-- Line
Figure <|-- Triangle
Figure <|-- Rectangle
Figure <|-- Square
Figure <|-- Circle
Figure <.. Vertex2D




@enduml
